'''Touchstones''' were small treats, made in various shapes, colors, sizes, textures, even temperatures. They could be placed into the mouth, to dissolve into flavors, or broken under the nose and inhaled. Some contained [[flower/Legends|flower]] scent, [[vanilla/Legends|vanilla]] [[syrup]] or [[cinnamon/Legends|cinnamon]]-flavored [[liqueur/Legends|liqueur]], found in star-, triangle- or sphere-shaped variations.

[[Jerec (Inquisitor)|Jerec]] was fond of them, not only for himself but also of giving bad-tasting ones to his subordinates, who he knew were too proud to refuse him.

One time he offered one to [[Sariss]] which released a stench, causing [[Boc Aseca]] to laugh at her.

